# decomp/mods/transplant/manifest
#
# Per-function override manifest for the transplant mod.
#
# Format: <function_symbol>  <override_file_path>
# Override paths are relative to this manifest's directory.
#
# Initial population is the port of the legacy whole-TU asm overlays
# under mods/transplant/race/*.s into per-function overrides. The
# bodies are byte-for-byte ports including their TRANSPLANT comments;
# only the wrapping changed (raw .s -> `int FUN_X(void) asm { ... }`
# under saturncc).
#
# Deferred (not yet ported):
#   * mods/transplant/race/FUN_0604D380.s -- the surgical 30-function
#     removal from ba9cf0de. Belongs with the "real removal" workstream
#     once Tier 1 splitter symbolicness lands; in the meantime the dead
#     functions remain pristine in race.bin (they are reachable bytes
#     but empirically dead callers, so functionally identical).
#   * mods/decomp/race/FUN_06037E28.c, FUN_06036BB8.c -- Cygnus C
#     overlays. These need re-translation to saturncc-compatible C
#     and are part of the lift-to-C track, not the asm-level mod port.

